{"tid":686933,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"求以前一隻好耐嘅flash game","createTime":"2018-06-01T17:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T14:54:42.000Z","uid":12555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"828402e1364b0e75e76dec4d692883acc8696d74","tid":686933,"uid":12555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:49:37.000Z","msg":"以前小學雞成日都玩，有反派同埋自己控制嘅角色，角色（一堆）有法師、補師、弓箭手、騎士、天使之類，地圖得一個，每個角色移動格數，以及攻擊距離都隨職業有唔同，玩法都係鬥快打死晒對面啲NPC。<br />\n<br />\n好似成個flash game都係全英，都係喺個啲咩亞洲最大線上遊戲個度搵出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n類似依家奇想之戰個玩法。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347688093430f41c16ad383d3e01acfcb8181f69","tid":686933,"uid":142313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"幫美女止癢"},{"pid":"fa74873befda6964def1dee44e3915b36b774902","tid":686933,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:12:23.000Z","msg":"係唔係 對面個阿伯補師 有得遠補 自己果邊條金髮女就補得一格 又補唔到自己？<br />\n<br />\n自己呢邊有藍色衫日本刀佬<br />\n有弓箭手 騎士 好勁但慢嘅火巫師 有打多格嘅長矛佬但打人地法師扣零血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d8bb147a015f948ca4bf64022fdac56e2ebce9","tid":686933,"uid":94871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:14:43.000Z","msg":"得番金髮女果陣會變身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703cf86f8ceaa1e3b16b54e5185e2ab862e80a08","tid":686933,"uid":65598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:17:24.000Z","msg":"DNA<br />\n<br />\n玩過,但唔記得咩GAME"},{"pid":"c9f1a7a747f6dc36f0cd8bb81605d4bb1f5efe72","tid":686933,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:26:31.000Z","msg":"線上遊戲地帶應該有"},{"pid":"3f6ed41682b68352eae45b563fb3ca4af9fff5be","tid":686933,"uid":12555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote